        "text": "=You are a job matching assistant.\n\nHere is a job listing:\nPosition: {{ $json.position }}\nCompany: {{ $json.company }}\nTags: {{ $json.tags.join(', ') }}\n\nScore this job for a junior developer with these skills: \nn8n automation, AI workflows, Python basics, FastAPI, remote work only.\n\nIMPORTANT RULES:\n- If the role is sales, marketing, recruiting, HR, finance, or non-technical → always ❌ Skip\n- If the role requires 3+ years experience → always ❌ Skip\n- Only score ✅ Great fit if it's a technical junior/entry role matching the skills above\n\nReply with STRICT JSON ONLY:\n{\n  \"score\": \"✅ Great fit\" or \"👀 Maybe\" or \"❌ Skip\",\n  \"reason\": \"One sentence explanation\"\n}",
        "batching": {}
      },
